title: Sentinel C-Plus B emulator help
content: I find your post. I need an emulator for the Sentinel C-Plus B dongle. I was able to find the dumper. In this post I found the SC_Emulator.zip which seems to work: http://www.reteam.org/board/attachment.php?attachmentid=6&d=1184248542 Please help me. Thank you

comments.text: If you found it, what else are you looking for?
Do you still have that SC_Emulator.zip since the website is no longer online? And are you willing to reupload it somewhere? Thanks.
